Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.47,0:01:19.13,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,止まらない夢を　君と君と　いつか　叶えられるなら
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.45,0:01:26.75,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,きっと強くなれる　時をかけるよ今！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.76,0:01:38.56,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,それはPreviousもなく出会う奇跡 Destiny
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.56,0:01:43.90,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,素顔を隠しながら　守るよ　もうひとりじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.36,0:01:49.04,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,わかってるんだずっと　その孤独を
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.40,0:01:54.40,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,Ah...　恐れないで　迷わないで　ありのままで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.83,0:01:59.76,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,約束する　必ず迎えに行く
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.49,0:02:05.19,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,届かない　明日は　高く高く　果てなく
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.39,0:02:11.22,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,目の前にあるReal　願いこの空に消えてく
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.58,0:02:17.13,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,止まらない　夢を　君が君が　いつか　ヒカリ望むなら
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.53,0:02:22.85,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,きっとたどり着く　時をかけるよ今！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.13,0:02:28.42,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,君を　君を　君を　守りたいから
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.32,0:02:32.78,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,I'll Be with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.47,0:01:19.13,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,如果將來能和你一起實現那永恆的夢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.45,0:01:26.75,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定能夠變強 現在就穿越時空吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.76,0:01:38.56,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,那是沒有預告的奇跡邂逅 是命運
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.56,0:01:43.90,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,戴上面具守護你 再也不會孤單
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.36,0:01:49.04,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直明白你的孤獨
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.40,0:01:54.40,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,啊..不要害怕 不要疑惑 做你自己吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.83,0:01:59.76,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,我向你保證 一定會去迎接你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.49,0:02:05.19,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,無法觸及的明天 高高在上無窮無盡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.39,0:02:11.22,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,眼前的現實讓願望消散在空中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.58,0:02:17.13,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你在永恆的夢中期盼光明來臨的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.53,0:02:22.85,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,你一定會到達那裏 現在就穿越時空吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.13,0:02:28.42,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我想要守護你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.32,0:02:32.78,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,我將與你同在
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.62,0:22:16.54,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,いつまでもキミの夢も明日(あす)も未来を
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.80,0:22:22.28,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,きっと強くなるよ Little*Lion*Heart
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.68,0:22:35.79,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,気持ちよダッシュして　どんなピンチも追い越せ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.98,0:22:41.14,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,キミを(きっと)すぐに(Soon you feel)もう安心だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.46,0:22:46.61,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,アイマイ弱いハート　限界超えの勇気は
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.85,0:22:52.21,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,いつも(今も)キミの(信号)キャッチ I am ready！！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.60,0:22:56.97,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,誰よりキミが大事だから
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.24,0:23:03.28,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,熱くなってく　さあこの心で戦える！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.28,0:23:07.70,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,キミの夢も明日(あす)も未来も
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.00,0:23:14.09,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,この手で絶対守るから　誓ったんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.09,0:23:18.49,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,どんな涙も拭いてあげる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.80,0:23:24.53,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,危なっかしいな　でも笑顔でまた困らせて？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.82,0:23:27.42,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,だってだって　まだまだ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.42,0:23:30.10,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,小さな勇者は
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.10,0:23:32.70,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,だってだって　もっともっと
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.70,0:23:37.83,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,強くなる Little*Lion*Heart
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.62,0:22:16.54,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,永遠守護你的夢想 你的明天 你的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.80,0:22:22.28,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,一定會變得更強大 幼獅雄心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.68,0:22:35.79,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,讓心情馳騁起來 超越各種危機
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.98,0:22:41.14,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,一定會馬上就讓你覺得安心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.46,0:22:46.61,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,曖昧弱小的心需要超越極限的勇氣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.85,0:22:52.21,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,隨時都能捕捉到你的信號 我準備好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.60,0:22:56.97,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,因為比誰都在乎你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.24,0:23:03.28,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,熱情不斷高漲 來吧 用這個心情去戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.28,0:23:07.70,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,你的夢想 你的明天 你的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.00,0:23:14.09,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,我發誓一定用這雙手來守護
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.09,0:23:18.49,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,幫你拭去所有的淚水
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.80,0:23:24.53,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,看著好擔心啊 但是你的笑容又讓人不知所措
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.82,0:23:27.42,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,因為因為 還沒結束
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.42,0:23:30.10,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,小小的勇者
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.10,0:23:32.70,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,因為因為 要變得
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.70,0:23:37.83,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,更強更強 幼獅雄心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.33,0:00:06.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這..這傢伙怎麼回事啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.83,0:00:22.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你沒有受傷吧？女士
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.47,0:00:33.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告辭了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.97,0:00:46.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Knight..Lancer
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.49,0:02:40.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是SilverLancer（白銀槍手）
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.74,0:02:49.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她是KnightLancer的英雄同伴 你看
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.63,0:02:56.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真..真緒醬 畫得真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.14,0:03:12.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是SunnyLancer（陽光槍手）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.11,0:03:16.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然是個還在修行的英雄 不過她是個努力家
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.87,0:03:19.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 真可愛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.74,0:03:22.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不不 這畫的是你啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.66,0:03:23.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.84,0:03:27.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個英雄的原型是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.01,0:03:52.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是RoseLancer（玫瑰槍手）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.22,0:03:57.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼事這麼好笑？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.48,0:03:59.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.16,0:04:04.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起 羽炎讓你費心了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.88,0:04:05.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.37,0:04:09.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真緒大人之事 雖然他是來謝罪的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.83,0:04:11.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過他在這裏的確是坐如針氈呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.61,0:04:15.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是讓他去迎接葉太郎而已
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.08,0:04:18.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,畢竟謝罪之事 少了葉太郎怎麼能算數
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.34,0:04:24.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼回事啊？這幫傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.58,0:04:38.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得趕緊通知老大..
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.51,0:04:43.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在被他知道可不行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.84,0:04:47.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ShadowSaber（暗影劍客）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.27,0:04:54.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和爸爸一樣 是正義的英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.10,0:04:55.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜歡嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.75,0:04:57.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.33,0:04:59.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.10,0:05:04.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想必那傢伙..你的師父也會高興的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.43,0:05:11.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,連你都..
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.57,0:05:15.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼..到底為了什麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.29,0:05:17.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多爾袞先生！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.06,0:05:24.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 葉太郎要什麼時候才會回來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.62,0:05:29.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為真緒醬不知道葉太郎大人是KnightLancer
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.03,0:05:32.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唉 畢竟羽炎也去接他了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.14,0:05:35.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真辛苦呢 KnightLancer
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.39,0:05:40.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真緒醬
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.24,0:05:43.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他一定馬上就會回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.93,0:05:47.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葉太郎君看到真緒大人的畫一定會高興的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.32,0:05:55.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎 說的也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.96,0:06:00.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起 葉太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.63,0:06:04.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多爾袞..先生..
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.91,0:06:16.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快點回來啊 葉太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.70,0:06:43.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天騎士部也不開張哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.37,0:06:46.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陽月學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.51,0:06:49.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這..這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.09,0:06:54.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個..
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.10,0:07:03.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是真的嗎？花房君他..失蹤的傳聞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.44,0:07:18.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.41,0:07:24.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真緒醬
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.13,0:07:25.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愛麗絲小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.02,0:07:28.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託你看家了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.01,0:07:32.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像找到了線索
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.61,0:07:37.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我..我也要一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.45,0:07:48.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.60,0:07:50.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愛麗絲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.56,0:07:54.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 為什麼最近沒有來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.82,0:07:57.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊不 我說那個..
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.35,0:07:59.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都很期待的說
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.70,0:08:12.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朱藤小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.59,0:08:17.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們找到了 多虧了大家的幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.00,0:08:25.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,依子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.44,0:08:38.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不會錯的 葉太郎他..人在鳳華島
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.77,0:09:11.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼事情會變成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.84,0:09:24.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,羽炎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.50,0:09:26.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你 你搞什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.97,0:09:29.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是想洗個澡而已..
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.69,0:09:30.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道有其他人在
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.58,0:09:33.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋笨蛋笨蛋 別到這邊來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.41,0:09:43.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞什麼啊 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.82,0:09:47.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們兩個 我這的澡堂不錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.21,0:09:55.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,館..館長？為什麼連館長也來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.82,0:10:00.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,羽炎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.30,0:10:05.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如何啊？我這最棒了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.48,0:10:07.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是..是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.31,0:10:09.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然這樣..
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.18,0:10:16.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就成為我的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.31,0:10:22.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成為我的人吧 葉太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.45,0:10:36.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愛麗絲小姐 之後的事拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.24,0:10:38.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.79,0:10:42.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把我..把我也帶上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.39,0:10:44.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.00,0:10:47.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們是要去葉太郎那裏吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.81,0:10:48.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼我也要去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.04,0:10:53.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 我不能帶真緒小姐去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.08,0:10:56.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,依子姐..
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.20,0:11:01.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真緒醬
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.27,0:11:03.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.60,0:11:36.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽的阻礙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.52,0:11:56.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 不可以打架
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.11,0:11:59.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 媽媽..
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.38,0:11:59.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不乖
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.59,0:12:03.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.75,0:12:04.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 不會..
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.98,0:12:06.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愛麗絲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.31,0:12:07.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.48,0:12:09.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.48,0:12:11.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真緒醬
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.95,0:12:16.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 騎士之事是秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.59,0:12:22.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真緒醬 為什麼這麼..
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.57,0:12:29.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託你 讓我去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.24,0:12:39.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我..想去葉太郎身邊..
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.33,0:12:45.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真緒醬..不..
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.94,0:12:52.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算我也..我也..
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.08,0:12:59.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想去葉太郎大人身邊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.67,0:13:10.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.45,0:13:25.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.86,0:13:28.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葉太郎的身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.95,0:13:29.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真緒醬
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.51,0:13:32.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.83,0:13:40.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,羽花
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.80,0:13:48.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞什麼嘛 那個大嬸真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.67,0:13:49.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.85,0:13:52.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼要道歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.41,0:13:54.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不也是被他們抓來的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.21,0:13:55.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.15,0:13:57.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以說為什麼..
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.15,0:14:00.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.28,0:14:02.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.48,0:14:07.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞什麼啊？為什麼澡堂裏會出現葉太郎和大嬸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.42,0:14:10.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葉太郎是我搞錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.67,0:14:12.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而館長的事我也..
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.94,0:14:13.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多爾袞先生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.18,0:14:22.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多爾袞先生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.02,0:14:34.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多爾袞先生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.93,0:14:36.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葉太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.82,0:14:39.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.56,0:14:44.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛痛痛..
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.46,0:14:52.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,溫泉有趣嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.59,0:14:56.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.22,0:15:10.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼..要這樣..
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.78,0:15:14.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,館長她打算把你列為她直屬的騎士
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.96,0:15:20.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她聽說你打敗了金剛寺先生 所以就..
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.16,0:15:22.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老大沒有輸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.64,0:15:23.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,羽炎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.86,0:15:25.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放開我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.69,0:15:29.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是這種事..太奇怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.38,0:15:50.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 久違了啊 這種氣息
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.12,0:15:56.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂 是女僕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.31,0:15:59.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,騎士之島連女僕都有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.14,0:16:03.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,騎士和女僕都是啥時代的事了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.77,0:16:21.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趕快逃比較好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.29,0:16:24.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這位女士是被稱為血之座天使的騎士
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.19,0:16:27.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是讓她心情不好的話..
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.09,0:16:29.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會死人的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.35,0:16:37.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀呀 害怕地都忘了同伴了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.80,0:16:39.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十分抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.77,0:16:43.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道朱藤小姐是騎士的人似乎變多了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.13,0:16:46.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好久不見了 基爾哈先生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.61,0:16:52.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請不要衝動 依子姐..
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.93,0:16:58.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果和四神..和館長的近衛騎士發生衝突的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.32,0:17:01.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就意味著要與全東亞區館為敵..
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.41,0:17:15.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還要一陣子才會到哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.85,0:17:20.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你 羽花
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.82,0:17:21.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不會
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.89,0:17:26.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是多虧了弟弟妹妹們的努力幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.01,0:17:30.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為大家都想救出家人..救出羽炎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.91,0:17:33.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.27,0:17:55.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒想到依子這麼快就介入了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.17,0:18:05.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您叫我嗎？館長
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.94,0:18:14.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葉太郎還不肯答應成為我的人麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.27,0:18:22.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,館長..這種做法果然還是..
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.17,0:18:31.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你啊 你以為依子會對葉太郎放手嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.14,0:18:33.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這..這個..
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.54,0:18:39.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.76,0:18:42.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由我去三兩下把他搞定
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.19,0:18:42.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.13,0:18:46.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葉太郎現在很混亂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.94,0:18:49.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少給他一點考慮的時間
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.16,0:18:59.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告訴基爾哈 讓他好好拖住她 明白了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.53,0:19:01.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.73,0:19:06.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,館長 就這麼想..
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.12,0:19:11.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把葉太郎..
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.30,0:19:42.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真慢呢 基爾哈哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.03,0:19:49.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,二位久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.51,0:19:53.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和館長聯絡過了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.66,0:19:55.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過她果然暫時回不來..
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.83,0:19:56.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,基爾哈先生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.30,0:19:58.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葉太郎先生在哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.47,0:20:01.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葉太郎君出什麼事了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.38,0:20:21.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 要在這種地方待到什麼時候
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.37,0:20:22.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.45,0:20:26.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以說就算你道歉也..
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.99,0:20:27.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎 算了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.78,0:20:31.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃飯了哦 葉太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.84,0:20:41.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起委屈你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.80,0:20:49.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼要對那種大嬸言聽計從啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.68,0:20:51.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也是騎士吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.41,0:20:56.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卻要被那種自說自話肆意妄為完全不顧他人的..
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.97,0:20:58.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不准說館長的壞話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.59,0:21:00.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多虧了館長
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.11,0:21:03.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我這樣的人也能勝任騎士之位
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.98,0:21:09.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多虧了館長給我的這個面具
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.42,0:21:14.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我..得以戰勝軟弱的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.37,0:21:17.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多爾袞先生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.04,0:21:21.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直以來..多虧面具我也..
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.09,0:21:25.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 我是為了遮掩騎士的身份
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.22,0:21:30.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,羽炎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.46,0:21:34.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葉太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.39,0:21:35.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好燙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.18,0:21:38.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快叫醫生來 快點
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.64,0:21:41.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我連累你一起受罪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.66,0:21:47.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少..至少讓你出去也好..
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.99,0:22:09.93,title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,525)}成為我的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.70,0:23:42.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噗溜歩 噗溜歩 噗溜溜歩
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.86,0:23:44.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白姬連迷蹤步都走得很棒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.81,0:23:45.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.35,0:23:47.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安靜 要是被發現就會被依子噗溜掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.66,0:23:50.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下回的槍假面是潛入任務
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.15,0:23:54.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我們要潛入依子的房間 找出她的把柄
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.67,0:23:56.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還..還是別去了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.00,0:23:56.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會被噗溜掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.84,0:23:59.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 你們倆真沒骨氣 做好覺悟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.16,0:24:00.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請問你們在做什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.36,0:24:04.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽我說聽我說 她們兩個想要潛入依子的房間呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.48,0:24:06.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白姬什麼都沒有干哦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.10,0:24:08.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白姬
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.26,0:24:09.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,背叛了
